Problem Name: Sending Vs Opening Snaps
Company: Ace teh Data Science Interview 
Difficulty Level: Medium
Link to Problem: https://datalemur.com/questions/time-spent-snaps
What did I learn? -- Using aggregate filtes in the select statement was something I had not done before

*/ 
SELECT 
"age_bucket" AS "Age Bucket", 
ROUND(100 * SUM("time_spent") FILTER (WHERE "activity_type" = 'send') / SUM("time_spent"),2) AS "Percent Spent",
ROUND(100 * SUM("time_spent") FILTER (WHERE "activity_type" = 'open') / SUM("time_spent"),2) AS "Percent Open"
FROM activities 
INNER JOIN age_breakdown ON activities.user_id = age_breakdown.user_id 
GROUP BY age_bucket 
